headline: Northern Trust Names Jordon Voss Pacific Northwest Region President
summary: SEATTLE, December 03, 2024--Northern Trust has appointed Jordon Voss as President of the Pacific Northwest Region. Voss will lead Northern Trust's Seattle-based team in the delivery of holistic advice and superior client service, while accelerating the growth of the wealth management business throughout Washington, Oregon and Idaho.
